    v1 = (wp.exp((v1 + 0.32 * v2 + 0.16)) * (v0 * (v2 + 0.59 * v0 + 0.92)))
    v0 = (wp.sin((v0 + 0.02 + v1 + 0.85)) / 0.73)
    v0 = 0.15
    v2 = wp.sin(wp.exp((v0 + 0.93 - v2 + 0.80)))
